channel.title: Downloading moparscape on windows
channel.description:
I downloaded moparscape on windows and it worked fine the first time; however when i went to start a server it would say "your account is already logged in" and i could never log in.
I decided to re-install but now it doesn't even install.
It comes up on my computer saying "download moparscape" so i click it, then install; however, when i install it just quits and doesn't install.
Is there a solution?
Thanks :)
